This documentation refers to appname version 0.0.1.

=head1 USAGE

    perl appname filename

Brief but working examples showing most common usage...

=head1 ARGUMENTS

A complete list of every argument that must appear on the command line when
the application is invoked, explaining what each one of them does, any
