example, many modules that use source code filters are mutually incompatible).

=over 4

=item L<Evil::Module>

If this application is used with L<Evil::Module> installed, things will blow up.

=back

=head1 BUGS AND LIMITATIONS

A list of known problems with the module, together with some indication of
